02/12/2005
ATHENS, Greece -- The head of the Public Power Corporation (PPC), Yiannis Paleokrassas, announced his resignation Thursday (1 December), after failing to provide evidence to support allegations of corruption he had leveled against other senior PPC officials. The cabinet had set a 1 December deadline for Paleokrassas to supply proof. (MPA, ANA - 01/12/05) 
